{"arkId":"cl010099953","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099953","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ronde","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ronde"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIV (1643-1715) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1685","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 1","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1685,"endYear":"","imprecision":"vers","text":"4e quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle = dernier quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Lucas, Jacques","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Lucas, Guillaume","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 8406","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Le fond du bo\u00eetier, entour\u00e9 d\u0027une frise grav\u00e9e, est d\u00e9coup\u00e9 \u00e0 jour de fins riceaux et grav\u00e9 au centre d\u0027une fleur \u00e0 cinq p\u00e9tales ; carr\u00e9s de remontage du mouvement et du r\u00e9veil de part et d\u0027autre de cette fleur centrale. Carrure grav\u00e9e et reperc\u00e9e d\u0027une frise continue de rinceaux fleuris semblables \u00e0 ceux du fond, bord\u00e9e d\u0027une bande de triangles. Lunette du verre grav\u00e9e de stries ; t\u00eate du pendant en forme de boule. Cadran, en argent sabl\u00e9, \u00e0 chiffres romains, des losanges polis indiquent les demi-heures ; au centre, le cercle mobile du r\u00e9veil porte des disques en argent poli o\u00f9 sont inscrits les chiffres arabes 1 \u00e0 11, l\u0027index \u00e0 la place du 12 indiquant les heures. Echappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre ; sonnerie de r\u00e9veil sur timbre ; rouage du r\u00e9veil en acier et le reste du mouvement en laiton dor\u00e9. Balancier muni d\u0027un ressort-spiral r\u00e9glant ; r\u00e9gulateur-cr\u00e9maill\u00e8re pr\u00e8s du coq, celui-ci \u00e0 un pied ajour\u00e9 de rinceaux sym\u00e9triques. Cliquet en partie disparu.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Lucas Amsterdam","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5,9","displayDimension":"5,9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"4,2","displayDimension":"4,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"3,8","displayDimension":"3,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,6","displayDimension":"2,6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)","placeOfCreation":"Amsterdam (Europe-\u003EPays-Bas = Pays Bas = Hollande)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Jules-Ren\u00e9 Olivier (1855-1933), horloger-collectionneur ; legs de sa s\u0153ur Marie-Julie Olivier, n\u00b0 764 ; comit\u00e9 du 24 janvier 1935 ; conseil du 5 f\u00e9vrier 1935 ; d\u00e9cret du 4 ao\u00fbt 1935 ; d\u00e9pos\u00e9e au mus\u00e9e des Arts d\u00e9coratifs le 4 novembre 1